                                </figure>
                            <div class="vert-align-title">
                                <h3 class="title"><span>Inside Three Companies That Are Innovating Flexible Schedules</span></h3>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                </a>
                </div>

                <div class="right-top">
                        <a class="" href="//www.fastcompany.com/3058955/startup-report/love-and-sex-are-a-swipe-away-but-finding-friends-digitally-is-still-hard">
                            <article class="story">
